Text:
If you haven't seen these videos then you owe it to yourself to download and watch them - the information they contain is truely astonishing.

As follow up, or maybe before even watching these, I'd recommend searching for downloading torrents related to the 'Disclosure Project' - can be got here:

https://thepiratebay.org/search/disclosure%20project/0/99/200

If you can't get this 'Energy' download to work (lack of seeds) then can download the 'flv' files here:

https://thepiratebay.org/torrent/5571190/The_Disclosure_Project_-_Alternative_Energy_Witness_Testimonies

Many thanks to the uploader.

Can also try the following for other energy stuff related to Steven Greer:

https://thepiratebay.org/search/steven%20greer/0/99/0
